{{#if isAuthenticated}}
    <h2> Hello {{user}}!</h2>
    <p>
      Click 'Jobs' to see your current list of job opportunities. From there
      you can view the details, delete or update job opportunity information.
    </p>
    <p>
      Click 'Create Job' to enter a new job opportunity.
    </p>
{{else}}
    <p>
      If you’re in active job search mode, you know that staying on top of
      all the job postings and follow-up tasks is not easy. If you
      don’t keep all those job opportunities organized, you're likely
      to slip up and slow down your progress.
    </p>
    <p>Help is here.</p>
    <p>
      Click Sign Up for a free trial. No credit card required, you don't even
      need to provide a real email address (in fact, we recommend that you
      don't).
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're already a member, please click on Sign In to begin slaying
      your job search!
    </p>
{{/if}}
